title: Working Through a Life Crisis
itunes:title: Working Through a Life Crisis
description:
At some point, almost everyone will wake up and think "How did I get here? This is not the life I wanted." It's an important part of our awakening. In this episode, I am going to talk about how to dig yourself out of the hole that you might find yourself in at some point in your life.
